metadata.name: Atago Taisho
metadata.description:
There are three benefits to joining 'TaishoDAO' free of charge.

(1) You get priority access to the "Sushi making Experience." Here, sushi masters/mistresses from 80 countries make sushi together.

(2) Receive priority guidance to experience newly developed sushi via social networking services.

(3) You will get priority to participate in a project promoted by the World Atago General to interview the world's best in some field while making sushi together, which will be broadcast on Youtube worldwide.
